WEBVTT

00:40.520 --> 00:45.160
[Ten days later]

01:54.070 --> 01:55.950
Long live Your Majesty!

03:23.420 --> 03:28.820
[[REBIRTH]]

03:29.320 --> 03:31.860
[Episode 39]

03:50.190 --> 03:51.079
Zhuge Yue,

03:51.630 --> 03:53.560
you claimed to the public that I was dead,

03:53.560 --> 03:55.020
yet kept me confined here,

03:55.630 --> 03:58.150
treating me like an honored guest,
well provided for.

03:58.150 --> 03:59.520
Going to such great lengths,

03:59.520 --> 04:01.120
what exactly do you want?

04:02.960 --> 04:05.520
The one who ordered your death
was Zhao Che.

04:06.080 --> 04:08.480
Qingshan Manor was only following orders.

04:08.630 --> 04:11.080
He has long coveted
the military power in the southwest.

04:11.080 --> 04:12.240
Only with your death

04:12.960 --> 04:15.870
can the Southwest Army
fully fall into his hands,

04:16.390 --> 04:17.269
General Meng.

04:18.670 --> 04:22.410
[General Meng, General of Southwest Army]

04:20.600 --> 04:24.070
His Highness wasn't like this back then.

04:24.750 --> 04:25.870
Things change.

04:26.750 --> 04:27.880
The Zhao Che of today

04:28.430 --> 04:30.120
is no longer who he once was.

04:30.720 --> 04:31.600
Now,

04:31.720 --> 04:32.950
all he sees is power.

04:33.270 --> 04:34.670
He wages war recklessly,

04:34.920 --> 04:36.800
bent on annexing Ximeng.

04:37.270 --> 04:38.070
Zhuge Yue,

04:38.390 --> 04:39.950
what exactly do you want?

04:40.180 --> 04:41.580
I hope you, General Meng,

04:42.159 --> 04:43.390
will stand on my side.

04:46.870 --> 04:47.630
Zhuge Yue,

04:48.630 --> 04:51.290
the Meng family
has been loyal for generations.

04:51.430 --> 04:53.830
I will never rebel with you.

04:54.040 --> 04:54.840
General Meng,

04:55.630 --> 04:57.290
I've never intended to rebel.

04:57.630 --> 05:00.070
I only want to change this corrupt world.

05:12.310 --> 05:14.970
The four noble families
are deeply entrenched.

05:15.000 --> 05:16.860
You can't shake their foundation

05:17.240 --> 05:19.100
by killing one or two patriarchs.

05:20.360 --> 05:23.120
This is a dangerous path.

05:28.560 --> 05:29.360
Lord Zhuge,

05:30.160 --> 05:31.270
can I trust you?

05:31.800 --> 05:32.680
General Meng,

05:33.190 --> 05:34.480
if your loyalty

05:34.870 --> 05:36.070
to Great Yong

05:36.720 --> 05:39.310
means loyalty to the Zhao family
and the throne,

05:39.310 --> 05:40.770
then I'm not to be trusted.

05:41.240 --> 05:44.040
But if it means loyalty
to the people of Great Yong,

05:44.480 --> 05:46.830
then you and I

05:47.430 --> 05:48.630
are in the same boat.

05:50.800 --> 05:52.130
What do you want me to do?

05:52.190 --> 05:54.480
I want you to help me stop Zhao Che

05:54.950 --> 05:57.270
and completely change Great Yong.

06:09.040 --> 06:09.770
General Chu.

06:10.950 --> 06:12.630
All our men are here.

06:13.750 --> 06:15.210
We'll split into 4 groups.

06:15.310 --> 06:18.240
When Zhao Che's procession
reaches the Temple of the Faceless God,

06:18.240 --> 06:20.070
we'll move in
from the southwest, northwest,

06:20.070 --> 06:21.870
southeast, and northeast,

06:21.870 --> 06:23.120
cut through the city's side streets,

06:23.120 --> 06:24.520
and surround the temple.

06:24.870 --> 06:25.630
Let's go!

06:34.610 --> 06:37.590
[Temple of the Faceless God]

06:35.800 --> 06:38.120
The new emperor is ascending
the throne here in Zhenhuangcheng,

06:38.120 --> 06:40.980
but outside the city,
we are surrounded by enemies.

06:41.070 --> 06:43.040
We lost the battle against Ximeng,

06:43.430 --> 06:45.040
and Biantang's army is also here.

06:45.040 --> 06:47.100
They are about to reach Baiquan Pass.

06:47.480 --> 06:48.360
You have no idea.

06:48.360 --> 06:51.560
I heard that after the new emperor performs
the sacrifice to the Faceless God today,

06:51.560 --> 06:54.159
he will deploy Quanrong's army
as reinforcements.

06:54.159 --> 06:55.040
Quanrong?

06:55.680 --> 06:58.190
Hasn't Great Yong always
considered Quanrong a major enemy?

06:58.190 --> 06:58.920
How could...

09:09.270 --> 09:10.670
Zhuge Yue!

09:11.240 --> 09:12.040
Your Majesty.

09:13.320 --> 09:16.050
Now I will answer the question
you asked that day.

09:16.870 --> 09:18.080
I am not your man,

09:18.550 --> 09:21.150
nor do I want
to be a loyal dog of Qingshan Manor.

09:21.390 --> 09:23.990
I took your side
and returned to Qingshan Manor

09:24.390 --> 09:26.590
just to rid Great Yong of people like you

09:27.080 --> 09:29.740
and your father—
a chronic illness to the state.

09:30.000 --> 09:30.670
Guards!

09:31.240 --> 09:32.670
Arrest Zhuge Yue!

09:39.550 --> 09:41.150
The guards outside right now

09:41.320 --> 09:43.250
are all spies from Qingshan Manor.

09:44.270 --> 09:46.960
From the day they entered Qingshan Manor,

09:47.390 --> 09:48.440
risking their lives,

09:48.440 --> 09:50.840
they've been nothing
but dogs in your eyes.

09:51.440 --> 09:52.200
Do you think

09:53.080 --> 09:54.360
at a time like this,

09:55.120 --> 09:57.580
they would still
be willing to fight for you?

09:59.630 --> 10:02.160
Prince of Jing will be here soon
to protect me.

10:02.600 --> 10:05.320
The Southwest Army
and Zhenhuangcheng's imperial guard

10:05.320 --> 10:06.780
are all under his command.

10:07.840 --> 10:10.200
Do you think Qingshan Manor's spies
can defeat them?

10:10.200 --> 10:11.670
Prince of Jing won't come.

10:12.550 --> 10:13.950
Because General Meng...

10:14.960 --> 10:16.150
is not dead.

10:22.750 --> 10:23.600
General Meng?

10:24.750 --> 10:25.790
Aren't you dead?

10:26.480 --> 10:28.270
I've disappointed you, Your Highness.

10:28.270 --> 10:29.150
I...

10:29.630 --> 10:30.490
am still alive!

10:30.600 --> 10:31.720
Everyone!

10:32.390 --> 10:34.270
Take down the rebels!

10:34.720 --> 10:35.440
Yes!

11:09.630 --> 11:10.840
Zhuge Yue,

11:11.720 --> 11:13.270
how dare you betray me!

11:13.670 --> 11:14.320
Zhao Che,

11:15.670 --> 11:17.870
you betrayed yourself first.

12:13.840 --> 12:14.600
Zhuge Yue.

12:16.070 --> 12:17.800
We have surrounded this place.

12:18.870 --> 12:21.130
The allied forces of Great Yan and Ximeng

12:21.510 --> 12:23.870
have also breached
Great Yong's defense line.

12:23.870 --> 12:24.670
Zhao Che,

12:25.200 --> 12:26.530
your defeat is certain.

12:27.000 --> 12:27.840
Today,

12:28.670 --> 12:31.530
I'd like to see
who in this Temple of the Faceless God

12:31.720 --> 12:33.270
is the true winner.

14:46.440 --> 14:47.510
Zhuge Yue...

14:49.240 --> 14:50.200
why?

14:53.510 --> 14:54.550
Xing.

14:56.670 --> 14:58.320
Because of Blood on Snow

14:59.270 --> 15:00.790
and the Huiyuan Pill,

15:01.910 --> 15:04.320
my heart meridian has long been damaged.

15:05.670 --> 15:08.630
You have a dream
of freeing slaves and ending wars.

15:10.320 --> 15:12.550
I want to use the last of my life

15:13.790 --> 15:15.960
to help you achieve that.

15:16.920 --> 15:19.760
Zhao Che is in the temple.

15:21.240 --> 15:23.240
As for the people of Qingshan Manor,

15:24.320 --> 15:26.920
I have already arranged
for their evacuation.

15:27.630 --> 15:28.390
Later,

15:29.840 --> 15:31.770
General Meng will come to help you.

15:33.150 --> 15:35.600
As long as you kill me, this sinner,

15:36.720 --> 15:38.750
the world will be united

15:40.150 --> 15:41.870
and a prosperous era of peace

15:43.720 --> 15:45.150
will arrive.

16:05.120 --> 16:06.080
Xing...

16:06.340 --> 16:09.880
♪ The dust in the world ♪

16:07.630 --> 16:08.910
Don't be sad.

16:10.320 --> 16:13.610
♪ Is blown away easily by the wind ♪

16:10.390 --> 16:11.870
Back in Ximeng,

16:12.870 --> 16:14.030
I knew

16:14.640 --> 16:17.360
♪ Who can stay calm ♪

16:15.320 --> 16:16.960
you wouldn't come with me.

16:18.120 --> 16:19.610
♪ And not be scared? ♪

16:18.270 --> 16:19.000
Because...

16:19.630 --> 16:21.600
♪ A slight ripple ♪

16:20.390 --> 16:21.870
you're Chu Qiao.

16:21.930 --> 16:25.520
♪ Floating life hangs by a thread ♪

16:23.720 --> 16:24.850
You are destined...

16:25.790 --> 16:28.120
not to be an ordinary woman.

16:25.800 --> 16:29.170
♪ The more pulled, the softer it gets ♪

16:29.910 --> 16:31.120
You'll walk

16:30.140 --> 16:32.980
♪ Who dares to say forever? ♪

16:32.390 --> 16:34.030
a much harder path.

16:33.650 --> 16:37.020
♪ Let it be ♪

16:36.360 --> 16:37.150
And I

16:38.100 --> 16:41.530
♪ Grudges and grace
were never meant to be ♪

16:40.440 --> 16:42.440
can only accompany you this far.

16:42.010 --> 16:45.020
♪ Why must you take and demand so much? ♪

16:44.600 --> 16:45.720
If I don't die,

16:45.400 --> 16:47.030
♪ Go weaving ♪

16:47.150 --> 16:49.960
Qingshan Manor
cannot be completely abolished.

16:47.360 --> 16:52.310
♪ Grand and glorious excuses ♪

16:51.960 --> 16:54.120
And the Zhuge family

16:53.140 --> 16:55.690
♪ We face ♪

16:55.270 --> 16:56.440
and the four noble families

16:55.710 --> 16:59.560
♪ The heavy thunderstorm together ♪

16:58.600 --> 17:00.600
cannot be brought down.

17:00.720 --> 17:03.450
♪ Even with extreme pain ♪

17:03.480 --> 17:08.240
♪ We don't even wince ♪

17:05.270 --> 17:06.109
Xing...

17:08.369 --> 17:10.920
♪ Why in this world ♪

17:09.240 --> 17:10.920
Don't be sad for me.

17:10.940 --> 17:16.060
♪ The staunchest heart
and strongest soul ♪

17:12.829 --> 17:14.680
Don't stop for me.

17:16.349 --> 17:17.790
Keep moving forward.

17:16.770 --> 17:23.220
♪ Yield so easily to gentle warmth? ♪

17:23.819 --> 17:26.619
♪ We once beheld ♪

17:26.640 --> 17:30.040
♪ A mirage on earth ♪

17:31.760 --> 17:34.400
♪ Beauty never ♪

17:34.430 --> 17:39.160
♪ Lasts for long ♪

17:39.430 --> 17:42.950
♪ No matter how a jade is carved ♪

17:42.970 --> 17:47.410
♪ It's just a stone ♪

17:47.710 --> 17:54.920
♪ It will eventually disappear ♪

17:55.680 --> 18:05.630
♪ It will eventually disappear ♪

18:37.180 --> 18:38.650
[Qingshan Manor]

18:44.160 --> 18:44.880
Miss Chu,

18:46.000 --> 18:48.200
before the Young Master left, he told me

18:48.790 --> 18:50.520
that Great Yong is beyond cure.

18:51.270 --> 18:53.400
If the noble families are not uprooted

18:53.510 --> 18:55.400
and a new government is not established,

18:55.400 --> 18:57.330
no matter who becomes the emperor,

18:57.750 --> 18:59.270
this world will not get better.

18:59.270 --> 19:00.070
So...

19:01.160 --> 19:03.020
he pretended to ally with Zhao Che

19:03.310 --> 19:06.200
to take the opportunity
to uproot the four noble families,

19:06.200 --> 19:07.660
and then strike at the root

19:08.200 --> 19:10.070
to eliminate Zhao Che's whole faction.

19:10.070 --> 19:11.110
Even for today,

19:12.240 --> 19:14.160
he had everything planned.

19:14.830 --> 19:16.270
The Young Master
ordered the people of Qingshan Manor

19:16.270 --> 19:17.590
to keep searching for you
and the King of Great Yan

19:17.590 --> 19:18.440
just to protect you

19:18.440 --> 19:20.270
before Zhao Che made his move.

19:20.510 --> 19:21.710
The Young Master said

19:21.920 --> 19:23.580
that once everything is done,

19:23.640 --> 19:25.510
the entire Great Yong
will see a new world.

19:25.510 --> 19:26.310
By then,

19:26.750 --> 19:28.440
it won't need the brothers
of Qingshan Manor

19:28.440 --> 19:29.310
to risk their lives,

19:29.310 --> 19:30.550
and the commoners

19:30.790 --> 19:33.390
and slaves will no longer
be treated like dirt.

19:33.750 --> 19:34.880
This is a shared wish

19:35.640 --> 19:36.770
between you and him.

19:38.720 --> 19:40.780
He wanted to present this world to you

19:41.830 --> 19:43.030
with his own hands.

20:03.300 --> 20:04.360
I don't believe it.

20:06.720 --> 20:08.350
He must have been lying to us.

20:09.070 --> 20:10.940
Even spies have ways to fake their deaths,

20:10.940 --> 20:12.050
let alone him.

20:19.240 --> 20:21.410
He must have wanted the world to think

20:22.840 --> 20:24.970
that the Zhuge family had truly fallen

20:25.720 --> 20:28.980
and that the four noble families
had really been wiped out.

20:29.000 --> 20:29.960
Right?

20:34.110 --> 20:34.810
Miss,

20:36.110 --> 20:38.310
the Young Master left you one last word,

20:38.460 --> 20:39.440
asking you not to blame him

20:39.440 --> 20:41.500
for making such a decision on his own.

20:41.720 --> 20:43.780
As long as you believe he hasn't left,

20:44.680 --> 20:46.000
he will, as always,

20:47.360 --> 20:49.160
stay behind you and protect you.

20:51.980 --> 20:52.700
Zhuge Yue!

20:55.920 --> 20:56.650
General Chu.

20:58.200 --> 20:59.070
General Xing.

20:59.790 --> 21:00.650
What happened?

21:06.440 --> 21:07.170
General Chu,

21:07.350 --> 21:08.960
an urgent report came from the border.

21:08.960 --> 21:10.550
The Quanrong people took the opportunity
of the marriage alliance

21:10.550 --> 21:12.720
and breached the northwest defense pass.

21:12.720 --> 21:14.650
The 100,000 troops lent to Zhao Che

21:14.750 --> 21:17.480
are massacring indiscriminately
in Great Yong.

21:19.030 --> 21:21.310
Once the Quanrong people enter Great Yong,

21:21.310 --> 21:22.440
not only Great Yong,

21:22.510 --> 21:25.680
but Great Yan and Biantang
will also be in grave danger.

21:26.440 --> 21:27.830
Besides fighting back,

21:28.400 --> 21:29.930
we have no other choice now.

24:04.400 --> 24:05.160
Chun'er...

24:10.030 --> 24:10.960
Li Yan.

24:13.880 --> 24:15.880
You are the only person in this world

24:20.720 --> 24:22.400
who has ever been good to me.

24:32.070 --> 24:33.000
Thank you.

25:53.070 --> 25:53.880
Zhao Che.

25:55.550 --> 25:57.480
You're here to mock me, aren't you?

25:57.830 --> 25:58.680
Today,

25:59.510 --> 26:01.970
I came to say goodbye
to an old acquaintance.

26:03.550 --> 26:04.750
An old acquaintance?

26:05.830 --> 26:06.590
Chu Qiao,

26:07.830 --> 26:10.240
why did you call me an old acquaintance?

26:12.110 --> 26:14.110
Zhao Chun'er opened the border pass

26:14.310 --> 26:16.310
and let the Quanrong people invade.

26:16.480 --> 26:17.440
I have decided

26:18.830 --> 26:20.030
to march into battle.

26:20.880 --> 26:21.680
Chun'er...

26:26.880 --> 26:27.590
Zhao Che.

26:29.790 --> 26:30.960
I was born a slave

26:31.550 --> 26:32.950
and grew up in Great Yong.

26:33.960 --> 26:34.820
Over the years,

26:35.920 --> 26:36.920
the people I knew—

26:37.830 --> 26:38.590
Zhao Song,

26:39.510 --> 26:40.240
Chun'er,

26:41.200 --> 26:41.920
Li Ce,

26:43.270 --> 26:44.330
and even Zhuge Yue—

26:45.310 --> 26:46.920
have all left me one by one.

26:47.160 --> 26:47.760
And you...

26:48.510 --> 26:50.970
are the only person
from my past in Great Yong

26:51.680 --> 26:53.070
who is still alive.

27:00.070 --> 27:00.880
Back then,

27:01.750 --> 27:04.000
I became the martial arts instructor
of Great Yong's imperial guard

27:04.000 --> 27:05.530
and was under your command.

27:05.960 --> 27:07.550
The Zhao Che I knew then

27:09.160 --> 27:10.690
was a righteous, decisive,

27:11.070 --> 27:13.200
and good general who loved his people.

27:15.240 --> 27:17.900
Great Yong's soldiers
couldn't stand the cold,

27:17.960 --> 27:20.440
so you personally supervised
the making of winter clothes

27:20.440 --> 27:22.070
and delivered them to the border soldiers

27:22.070 --> 27:23.720
with your own hands.

27:25.200 --> 27:26.130
I also remember,

27:26.750 --> 27:28.410
to reduce the people's taxes,

27:28.680 --> 27:31.210
you argued strongly
with the court officials

27:31.350 --> 27:33.350
and almost lost command of the army.

27:42.960 --> 27:43.680
I remember

27:44.590 --> 27:46.510
you personally received the wounded

27:46.510 --> 27:47.840
in the winter blizzard,

27:48.550 --> 27:51.400
completely ignoring
the frostbite on your feet.

27:52.880 --> 27:54.210
The Zhao Che of that time

27:55.000 --> 27:56.310
was a general

27:57.030 --> 27:58.690
we were all willing to follow.

28:01.720 --> 28:02.440
I know

28:03.270 --> 28:05.270
you didn't want to become like this.

28:06.240 --> 28:08.300
If you hadn't been pushed to the edge,

28:08.830 --> 28:10.890
you would have been a very good person

28:11.440 --> 28:12.770
and a very good general.

28:13.000 --> 28:13.590
Enough!

28:15.550 --> 28:18.550
Why do you have to say
such heart-piercing words to me?

28:26.720 --> 28:28.050
I have no other purpose.

28:28.440 --> 28:31.170
I just want to say goodbye to you
for the last time.

28:32.110 --> 28:32.790
Zhao Che.

28:34.920 --> 28:35.790
Once I go,

28:37.480 --> 28:39.480
I'm not sure if I can come back alive.

28:39.790 --> 28:41.830
Besides Yan Xun and He Xiao, you are

28:42.400 --> 28:44.530
the only person I still have ties with.

28:44.590 --> 28:46.120
I just wanted to talk to you.

28:55.640 --> 28:56.350
Chu Qiao!

29:04.680 --> 29:05.790
Give me a chance.

29:07.240 --> 29:08.240
What chance?

29:08.920 --> 29:10.650
Please let me go to war with you.

29:12.790 --> 29:14.920
I am willing to be an ordinary soldier.

29:15.510 --> 29:16.790
I will charge at the very front

29:16.790 --> 29:19.050
and face any danger without hesitation.

29:20.440 --> 29:21.920
I know my sins are so grave

29:22.350 --> 29:23.880
that I can never repay them.

29:24.790 --> 29:26.920
But I just want to protect this land,

29:29.510 --> 29:30.590
to atone

29:31.070 --> 29:32.470
for all the people

29:33.510 --> 29:34.640
I have ever let down.

29:36.110 --> 29:36.790
Chu Qiao.

29:37.350 --> 29:38.750
I, Zhao Che, am a general.

29:40.440 --> 29:41.480
Even if I die,

29:42.830 --> 29:44.630
I should die on the battlefield.

29:56.870 --> 29:59.170
[Great Yong]

30:03.350 --> 30:04.070
Zhuge Yue.

30:04.880 --> 30:07.160
Today, Ximeng, Great Yong,

30:06.560 --> 30:08.980
♪ Facing the wind, I tread through frost ♪

30:06.800 --> 30:08.310
[Great Yan]

30:07.660 --> 30:09.900
Great Yan, and Biantang
have all mobilized their armies.

30:09.030 --> 30:12.410
♪ Measuring rivers and hills,
hooves rise light ♪

30:10.750 --> 30:13.830
This battle is not for past grievances,

30:13.340 --> 30:15.400
♪ The horizon lies far ahead ♪

30:14.680 --> 30:16.790
but to protect our common homeland.

30:15.770 --> 30:18.150
♪ Swaying gently ♪

30:17.270 --> 30:18.700
[Biantang]

30:19.640 --> 30:24.000
Fight the Quanrong invaders!

30:19.930 --> 30:22.160
♪ Through pine mists, past 1,000 hills ♪

30:22.190 --> 30:25.580
♪ Wrapped in the vast moonlight ♪

30:24.000 --> 30:28.830
Fight the Quanrong invaders!

30:26.340 --> 30:29.060
♪ Having drunk the surging waves ♪

30:29.140 --> 30:31.770
♪ I care not how far the road ♪

30:30.440 --> 30:41.720
Fight the Quanrong invaders!

30:33.740 --> 30:36.150
♪ When I was young ♪

30:36.170 --> 30:39.230
♪ I wrote poems
praising the prosperous world ♪

30:39.400 --> 30:42.570
♪ The wind was not yet full,
the moon not yet round ♪

30:41.920 --> 30:43.030
Behind me

30:42.590 --> 30:46.620
♪ Rushing me to charge forward ♪

30:43.480 --> 30:44.310
stand He Xiao,

30:44.790 --> 30:45.720
Zhao Che,

30:46.000 --> 30:47.530
and thousands of soldiers.

30:47.590 --> 30:49.190
♪ Strong wine to the wild plains ♪

30:48.640 --> 30:49.880
Let's go!

30:49.220 --> 30:51.030
♪ Beyond the pass,
sand blows like arrows ♪

30:51.040 --> 30:52.550
♪ I ride my horse toward the south ♪

30:52.580 --> 30:54.330
♪ Endless spring beneath my hooves ♪

30:54.360 --> 30:55.750
♪ Hoofbeats fade away ♪

30:55.910 --> 30:57.470
♪ Rolling over peaks and ridges ♪

30:57.590 --> 31:00.800
♪ A single neigh echoes
between heaven and earth ♪

31:00.850 --> 31:02.850
♪ Chasing the bright moon ♪

31:04.000 --> 31:07.160
♪ My spirit swallows
mountains and rivers ♪

31:27.720 --> 31:28.680
As history records,

31:28.680 --> 31:31.000
the Quanrong invaders
took advantage of our weakness

31:31.000 --> 31:32.800
and invaded the Central Plains.

31:33.430 --> 31:35.840
I'm not playing with you anymore.

31:37.640 --> 31:39.640
General Chu took the lead,

31:40.160 --> 31:42.000
uniting the forces of Ximeng, Great Yan,

31:42.000 --> 31:44.440
Biantang, and Great Yong,

31:44.590 --> 31:47.250
and finally defeated the Quanrong
completely!

31:53.790 --> 31:54.830
Zhuge Yue?
